casebody.data:
Patricia ALDRICH and Wendy McKnight, Personal Representative of the Estate of Judith Ann Kelly, Plaintiffs-Appellants,
v.
OHM SPECIALTY PHARMACY, LLC d/b/a Downs Pharmacy, Defendant-Appellee,
and
Chidozie Joshua Ononuju, D.O., Ramon Rodriguez, M.D., and American Medical Missionary Care, Inc., Defendants. SC: 158778
COA: 338140 Supreme Court of Michigan. May 29, 2019

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the October 23, 2018 judgment of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the questions presented should be reviewed by this Court.
